## Security Best Practices

- **Never expose API keys** in responses or logs — mask them in error messages
- **Validate userId** against the authenticated session before loading client profile — never trust user-supplied userId from the request body
- **Sanitize tool outputs** before including them in the LLM context — strip HTML if fetching web content
- **Rate-limit** agent invocations per user to prevent abuse
- **Firestore security rules** must restrict `clients/{userId}` reads to the authenticated user only

