## Development Workflow

- Feature branches follow the standard `<TICKET_ID>-<description>` convention
- New tools must be registered in `agentExecutor.ts` and documented here
- Any change to Firestore schema must update both this document and `ai-specs/specs/data-model.md`
- Run `npm run test:coverage` before opening a PR — 80% threshold enforced
